{"tid":1552870,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"如氦氣球飄起觸到鐵路電纜，會引致電力短路，可能會引起小火，導致電力供應系統「跳掣」，引發交通大災難","createTime":"2019-09-08T12:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T12:39:21.000Z","uid":301329,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0519223bc0008add21bf0e8079c7faa4ac239038","tid":1552870,"uid":301329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:21:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140203/00410_097.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140203%2F00410_097.html&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=3d351c58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140203/00410_097.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb497708b5616a8158d524c304c1b901cc8963d","tid":1552870,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:22:53.000Z","msg":"如果有運狗車出事會點，千祈唔好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d4a31a28cc5e86767949cedc1d956687e49ca7","tid":1552870,"uid":301329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bb497708b5616a8158d524c304c1b901cc8963d","tid":1552870,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:22:53.000Z","msg":"如果有運狗車出事會點，千祈唔好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:29:50.000Z","msg":"無錯！金屬氣球會令到港鐵癱瘓<br />\n千祈唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ab51c4d8df03fe157ba569b45e78ae79251354","tid":1552870,"uid":301329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:39:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20140129/52140353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140129%2F52140353&d=B3EKmdPj7R9OdkVaiVXMK5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=7a6de232\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140129%2F52140353&h=7fac09e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20140129/52140353</a><br />\n<br />\n金屬氣球熱賣搭港鐵記住唔好帶<br />\n<br />\n柴灣站今早有金屬氣球闖入路軌電範圍，令列車服務輕微受阻。其實過往每逢有年宵市場，氫氣球都成為熱賣貨品，不少市民會攜帶乘港鐵，前年1月長沙灣至美孚段的架空電纜供電系統安全裝置啟動，事後在列車車頂發現金屬氣球殘餘物，疑與事件有關。<br />\n<br />\n理工大學機械工程學系工程師盧覺強稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">若果金屬氣球升上令兩條電纜接上，引致電力短路，有機會發生小火或小爆炸，令安全裝置啟動，影響列車服務。</span><br />\n<br />\n大家帶金屬氣球千祈唔好入狗鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}